{
  "stem": "1603.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Like a German to kill a Jew was a-- a duty, and to these people, to save a life of a kid, they felt it was their duty.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, they didn't, and I don't think they had to know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, if you go on the street and it's raining and it's dark and you see a small kid sitting on the street there alone crying, don't you think it's your duty that you should go there and find out what is the problem and can you help, even you don't know that little kid?",
      "word_count": 56
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, that's how I feel that-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No, but I thought about it that-- that-- I thought about it writing-- writing a small play about this, you know?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And because it was a very, very touching and interesting experience.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And many things I do not recall as what was going on, but-- but I could concentrate, and I could think on it, and it would make a very interesting statement.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And but if I ever would write a play about this, then I would-- I would have everybody die at the end.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I wouldn't-- because then people would think that this whole thing was a happy ending kind of affair.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In this bakery or generally speaking?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Well, I had recollection of people joking around and trying to forget.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The adults were trying to kind of talk and everything like everything would be normal and Germans don't exist and these kind of things, you know, to bring themselves to a better mood and to relax and so on and so on.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After the bombing, after it happened.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the bombing was constantly going on.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
